---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - EU Peaks">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="min-h-screen py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Us</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none" style="text-wrap: pretty; orphans: 2; widows: 2;">
        <section class="mb-12">
          <div class="mb-6 flex justify-center">
            <img 
              src="/images/us/IMG_6771.jpeg" 
              alt="Nikolay and Maria on a mountain adventure" 
              class="rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-full h-auto max-h-96 object-cover"
            />
          </div>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Who We Are</h2>
          
          <p>
            We are Nikolay and Maria, an adventure duo passionate about mountaineering and exploration. As hiking buddies 
            and travel companions, we're embarking on an ambitious journey to climb the highest peak in each of the 27 
            European Union member countries. From the towering Alps to the rolling hills of Denmark, each summit represents 
            a unique challenge and story that we're excited to share with you.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            This blog documents our shared adventure as we work together to conquer Europe's highest peaks. 
            Each mountain offers its own set of challenges, and we believe that the journey is just as important 
            as the destination. Through teamwork, perseverance, and a shared love of the outdoors, we're making 
            memories one summit at a time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">What You'll Find Here</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Detailed Trip Reports:</strong> In-depth accounts of each climb with route information, conditions, and personal experiences</li>
            <li><strong>Photography:</strong> High-quality images capturing the beauty and challenge of each peak</li>
            <li><strong>Video Content:</strong> Links to YouTube videos documenting key moments and summits</li>
            <li><strong>Practical Information:</strong> Tips, gear recommendations, and logistical advice for fellow adventurers</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 text-center">The Adventure Continues</h2>
          <p>
            Each peak we conquer together brings new perspectives, challenges overcome, and memories made as a team. 
            Follow along as we work toward completing this ambitious goal, supporting each other every step of the way, 
            one summit at a time.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Prevent orphaned words and improve text flow */
  .prose p,
  .prose li {
    text-wrap: balance;
    text-balance: balance;
    hyphens: auto;
    word-spacing: 0.1em;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  /* For browsers that support text-wrap: pretty, use it for better line breaking */
  @supports (text-wrap: pretty) {
    .prose p,
    .prose li {
      text-wrap: pretty;
    }
  }
  
  /* Additional spacing adjustments */
  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }
</style> 